content.text: Quick update - I weigh 175 pounds now. The keto diet is really working. Lost 10 pounds in the last month.
That's great progress, Alex! Down to 175 from 185 - 10 pounds in a month on keto is solid. The gym routine is clearly paying off too.
Also I sold the Tesla and got a 2025 Rivian R1S. Needed more space for camping with Max. And I switched from keto to a Mediterranean diet - my doctor recommended it.
Big changes! Rivian R1S is perfect for camping and adventures with Max. And Mediterranean diet on the doctor's recommendation - that's a healthy pivot. I'll update everything.
